  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Sauté onions, garlic, and ginger until softened.",
    "Add curry paste and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add tomatoes, broth, sugar, turmeric, salt, and pepper.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in coconut milk and continue to simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve over rice or with naan bread."
